OL,3,CMan in his 80s dies after crashing
OL,4,Cinto parked car
OL,6,FA driver in his 80s has died after he
OL,7,Fcrashed into a parked car on a
OL,8,Fresidential street in Lancashire.
OL,10,FPolice said his Citroen C1 hit another
OL,11,Fvehicle on Carrwood Drive in Kirkham
OL,12,Fshortly after 2pm on Saturday.
OL,14,FThe man was pronounced dead at the
OL,15,Fscene while his female passenger
OL,16,Fescaped injury.
