OL,3,CMan in his 80s dies after crashing
OL,4,Cinto parked car
OL,6,FOfficers have launched an
OL,7,Finvestigation into the fatal collision
OL,8,Fand are urging anyone who witnessed
OL,9,Fthe incident, or captured it on
OL,10,Fdashcam or CCTV, to come forward.
OL,12,FDet Con Simon Grounds said: "Sadly a
OL,13,Fman has lost his life and I would
OL,14,Fappeal to anyone who saw what happened
OL,15,For who has any footage to get in
OL,16,Ftouch."
